<!-- WHY IRON ALONE ISN'T ENOUGH -->
<section class="s symptoms-bg">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="s-head center">
      <span class="s-eyebrow">The hidden pregnancy crisis</span>
      <h2 class="s-title">Why <em>iron alone</em> isn't enough.</h2>
      <p class="s-sub">Conventional iron tablets are harsh, poorly absorbed, and miss the co-factors your body needs to actually use the iron. Here's what most moms quietly live with.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="symptoms-grid">
      <div class="symptom-card"><div class="ic"><!-- battery-low --><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="7" width="17" height="10" rx="2.4"/><path d="M22 11v2"/><rect x="4.5" y="9.5" width="3.5" height="5" rx="1" fill="currentColor" stroke="none"/></svg></div><h4>Constant fatigue</h4><p>Tired despite sleep — the silent first sign of low iron in pregnancy.</p></div>
      <div class="symptom-card"><div class="ic"><!-- stomach waves --><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M3 9c2.5-2.5 5.5-2.5 8 0s5.5 2.5 8 0M3 14c2.5-2.5 5.5-2.5 8 0s5.5 2.5 8 0M3 19c2.5-2.5 5.5-2.5 8 0s5.5 2.5 8 0"/><circle cx="8" cy="5" r="1.2" fill="currentColor" stroke="none"/><circle cx="15" cy="5" r="1.2" fill="currentColor" stroke="none" opacity=".55"/></svg></div><h4>Nausea + constipation</h4><p>Ferrous sulfate causes GI side-effects in 50-80% of pregnant women.</p></div>
      <div class="symptom-card"><div class="ic"><!-- droplet through filter --><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 2.5c-2 3-5.5 7-5.5 10.5a5.5 5.5 0 0 0 11 0c0-3.5-3.5-7.5-5.5-10.5z"/><path d="M9.5 14c.7 1 1.5 1.5 2.5 1.5" opacity=".55"/><circle cx="12" cy="20" r="1.2" fill="currentColor" stroke="none"/></svg></div><h4>Poor absorption</h4><p>Most iron salts are absorbed at 5-10%. The rest passes right through.</p></div>
      <div class="symptom-card"><div class="ic"><!-- cloud / brain fog --><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M7 17h10a4 4 0 0 0 .8-7.9 5.5 5.5 0 0 0-10.7-.6A3.5 3.5 0 0 0 7 17z"/><path d="M5 20.5h4M11 20.5h3" opacity=".55"/></svg></div><h4>Brain fog</h4><p>Less oxygen to the brain — focus, memory and clarity all dip.</p></div>
